How to install

1) Do
	setenv ROOT <<root directort>>
	setenv JSFROOT <<jsf directort>>
	set path=($JSFROOT/bin $ROOTSYS/bin $path)

2) Edit pathname for perl and wish specified in the bin/mkbs and bin/buildjsf .
3) cd to src, and xmkmf ; make  -> this will create lib/libJSF.a and bin/jsf
4) cd example ; xmkmf ; make    -> this will create sample program.

that's it.